                    </div>
                    <span class="font-mono text-xs text-zinc-400 uppercase tracking-wider">Updated: November 2024</span>
                </div>

                <h1 class="font-serif text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-medium tracking-tight text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 mb-8">
                    Now
                </h1>
                
                <div class="prose prose-zinc dark:prose-invert max-w-none leading-relaxed">
                    <p class="text-xl font-light text-zinc-600 dark:text-zinc-300">
                        Currently working as a <strong>Senior Frontend Engineer</strong> at Tech Corp, focusing on building scalable design systems.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 mt-16 border-t border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-900 pt-12">
                
                <!-- Building -->
                <div class="space-y-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-2 text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100 font-serif font-bold text-lg">
                        <Zap size={18} />
                        <h3>Building</h3>
                    </div>
                    <ul class="space-y-2 text-sm text-zinc-500 dark:text-zinc-400">
