                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-start gap-4 p-4 rounded-xl bg-zinc-50 dark:bg-zinc-900 border border-zinc-100 dark:border-zinc-800">
                        <div class="w-12 h-16 bg-zinc-200 dark:bg-zinc-800 rounded shadow-sm flex-shrink-0"></div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-medium text-zinc-900 dark:text-zinc-100">Designing Data-Intensive Applications</div>
